    "title": "Job Opening Category Manager at Blue Dart Digital Technologies",
    "description": "Blue Dart Digital Technologies, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Category Manager for our Jabalpur operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Blue Dart Digital Technologies:\nBlue Dart Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in Influencer Marketing\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Referral bonus program\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Learning & development budget\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jabalpur, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Blue Dart Digital Technologies!",
